Scenario: Serialize Tender XML
Given I have a XmlSerializer for Tender
When I have an Tender xml:
<Tender TenderType="Cash" TypeCode="Sale">
    <Amount>500</Amount>
</Tender>
Then I should get Tender:
|amount|typecode|tendertype|
|500|Sale|Cash|

Scenario: Serialize Tender XML
Given I have a XmlSerializer for Tender
When I have an Tender xml:
<Tender TenderType="CreditDebit">
    <Amount>200</Amount>
     <Authorization>
      <AuthorizationCode>1234567</AuthorizationCode>
     </Authorization>
     <CreditDebit CardType="Credit">
       <ExpirationDate>2011-10</ExpirationDate>
       <CreditCardCompanyCode>1234</CreditCardCompanyCode>
     </CreditDebit>
</Tender>
Then I should get Tender:
|amount|authorizationcode|tendertype|cardtype|expirationdate|creditcardcompanycode|typecode|
|200|1234567|CreditDebit|Credit|2011-10|1234||
